    public interface WebModel
extends Serializable
    The interface for objects that store user specific session state for web components. The WebComponent and WebModel interfaces are not normally used directly, they just identify some common features between WComponents and InterceptorComponents.
    Since:
    1.0.0
    Author:
    Martin Shevchenko
